  "signal_description": "The query retrieves data from the table 'defaultview-225'. It calculates the month, number of cases, and average cycle time for each month. The 'Month' column is derived by truncating the 'END_TIME' column to the month level. The 'No. of Cases' column counts the number of 'CASE_ID' values. The 'Avg. Cycle time' column calculates the average time difference between the last 'end_time' for events with the name 'Clear Invoice' and the first 'end_time' for events with the name 'Vendor Creates Invoice'. The result is ordered by the 'Month' column in ascending order. The 'FILL timeseries('MONTH')' function is used to fill any missing months in the result with zero values."
}
